snippet: A South Carolina father who authorities said killed his five children believed the kids "were going to kill him, chop him up and feed him to the dogs," according to an unredacted arrest warrant released Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Warrant: SC Dad Feared 5 Slain Kids Would Kill Him
headline.main: Warrant: SC Dad Feared 5 Slain Kids Would Kill Him

lead_paragraph: A South Carolina father who authorities said killed his five children believed the kids "were going to kill him, chop him up and feed him to the dogs," according to an unredacted arrest warrant released Wednesday.
